# Backend

## Stack
FastAPI, SQLite (MVP), Hermes client, deterministic pipeline modules in Python

## Expected endpoints
- `GET /documents`
- `POST /documents/upload`
- `GET /documents/{id}`
- `GET /documents/{id}/followups`

## Hermes boundary
- Skills return reasoning/extraction only
- Deterministic pipeline sets status, scores, validation, DB writes, exports
- Keep FastAPI changes explicit and simple
- Do not invent endpoints without clearly labeling TODO/mock
